description: I don´t like cats so much. This guy even had two cats at home. And the whole apartment looked like a mess. During our meeting even his roommate appeared and disturbed me. Finally able to talk about his debts I realized that he had many smaller amounts that were already overdue. And here in the Czech Republic late payments can result in very high fines. So I offered him my all-inclusive package. I even offered him more by telling that there is a minimum amount for the loan. At a high interest rate of course. And then I introduced him to my special offer. I wanted his straight and hairy ass so much. He thought about it a lot. But finally he had to accept his probably last chance to get rid of all the debts before it was too late.
title: Debt Dandy 94
